Integrated a realistic typing indicator ("ZenBot is typing...") to simulate a human-like response delay.
API Communication:

Set up fetch() calls to communicate with a backend endpoint (/chat) for bot responses.
Error Handling:

Added fallback messages if the backend fails to respond.
